<div class="post-date">Sep  3</div>
<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=1145" title="We&#39;re ducks with our wings clipped"> We&#39;re ducks with our wings clipped</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>Over the last few days I have been beyond myself in anger. I have never seen this absolute level of incompetence and negligence from our government. The days we let people suffer unimaginable pain and death.</p>

	<p>Having seen this I now have the horrible knowledge that our government is broken. Knowing that our country is a sitting duck with our wings clipped. This is the government we get for cutting taxes and giving away billions upon billions to already stinking rich corporatiions while cutting government to pay for a war of choice. We get a government that can&#8217;t address basic functions of government.</p>

	<p>The Federal Emergency Management Agency once had been a pretty efficient agent for dealing with disasters. They were able to martial resources and get them on the ground. But after 9-11 the agency was butchered and merged into the Department of Homeland Security. This was the first test of the system that was supposed to protect our security and it failed so miserably that if I were a teacher I couldn&#8217;t even give them an F because that might mean they might got 50 percent of things right. </p>

	<p>I&#8217;d give them a 0 because not only did they refuse to respond, they repeatedly turned away help. They refused to let the Red Cross into New Orleans, they refused help from experienced boaters in the search efforts, they refused water-bombers from the U.S. Forest Service to quell the fires in New Orleans, they have refused skilled help from other countries and the list goes on. It&#8217;s like a like a rural fire company trying to single handedly deal with a massive forest fire and turning away help.</p>

	<p>Even worse is they knew this was coming. </p>

	<p>Everyone and their brother knew the levees would be overwhelmed in this situation. It was in the media, it was discussed repeatedly by government and by the meteological community. Hell, these levees were only designed to withstand a cat 3 hurricane! They knew at least two days in advance that a category five hurricane was coming to New Orleans (we lucked out that it was a four.)</p>

	<p>New Mexico Governor Bill Richardson &#8220;got it.&#8221; He offered his National Guard before the hurricane hit and Gov. Blanco accepted immediately because she knew 40 percent of her guard was in Iraq. But why were they not on the ground? Washington didn&#8217;t sign the orders until FOUR DAYS after the hurricane hit!</p>

	<p>This <a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/09/03/AR2005090301653.html">list goes on and on and on</a>. Just pay attention. Even Fox has outlined the problems here. Read <a href="http://www.dailykos.com">Daily Kos</a>, read anything and you&#8217;ll see the truth.</p>

	<p>This incompetance is absolutely criminal and it now seems that only the grace of the Good Lord will help us from here on out. Our government is broken and someone will pay!</p>


 
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="smallcat">Posted in <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?c=On-the-News">On-the-News</a></div>
